data.title: FUEL MOTORCYCLES
data.meta_description: Fuel’s vision for a community of nostalgic riders evolved over the years. They started designing stylish riding gear that blends vintage looks from the past with all the innovations of modern technology; the high-quality retro clothing that they wanted to wear, but couldn’t find on the market. data.text:
The Rally 2 Jacket represents a significant upgrade in both technical prowess and functionality compared to its predecessor. Designed for comfort and protection in any weather, it's your go-to for adventures. Stay dry in the rain, warm with the removable liner, and safe with built-in protections. Let nothing hold you back from chasing your dreams and discovering the extraordinary.

The Rally 2 Jacket is meticulously designed and crafted for touring and adventure enthusiasts, ensuring that you can travel through different climates or countries without being hindered by rain or cold.

The outer layer of the jacket is constructed from 500D Nylon with a PU coating for water repellency. For added protection during heavy rainfall, the jacket features a waterproof Tricot TPU seam-sealed membrane that hangs inside the outer shell (drop liner), keeping you completely dry. This method of construction provides an exceptional level of comfort on those long days on the road or trail.

When temperatures drop, just put on the removable 3 layer laminated softshell liner. It will keep you warm and dry, serving as a versatile standalone piece you can wear even when you’re not on the motorcycle.

As for protection and your peace of mind, our gear includes top-of-the-line D3O® brand level 1 protections delivering a high level of security for all your adventures.

This Jacket is CE certified at AA Level.

Introducing the Bunker Jacket, a 3/4-length jacket inspired by military and early motorcycle jackets. This rugged jacket is crafted from wet wax repellent canvas and reinforced with 100% polyester 300D in areas most susceptible to falls.

For the coldest seasons, its classy removable winter down lining guarantees warmth and comfort, rendering it a versatile garment that you can wear perfectly even when you’re off your motorcycle.

In essence, the Bunker Jacket is a timeless piece that will never go out of style, designed to last a lifetime. Discover the perfect blend of heritage and modern functionality with this jacket.

Crafted from wet wax repellent canvas

Additionally, the inclusion of a waterproof membrane between the outer fabric and lining results in an ideal jacket for wet weather conditions.

Quilted jacket included

A classy removable winter down lining guarantees warmth and comfort, rendering it a versatile garment that you can wear perfectly even when you’re off your motorcycle.

CE AAA Certified

The jacket has obtained the AAA certification, which is the highest in safety, and it also includes the high-quality 3DO protections for an additional layer of security.

TOP FEATURES

Adjustable neck with an original fastening system with an elastic strap for more comfort.

Main front metallic YKK zipper and hidden snap buttons to fix.

Sleeve ventilation openings.

Chest waterproof pocket.

Waterproof membrane between outer fabric and lining.

D3O Ghost CE-LEVEL 1 for shoulders, elbows and back

Removable winter down lining

CE AAA Certified for the highest in safety.

Tech Specs:

- Outer fabric: wet wax water repellent canvas 40% polyamide, 60% cotton.

- Shoulder and elbow panels reinforced with polyester 300D for enhanced abrasion resistance.

- Twill lining fabric 98% cotton, 2% spandex.

The Safari Jacket is inspired by the jackets of the first explorers to reach the unknown continents. It is the perfect companion for all your adventures in the wildest places of the world.

A 3/4 jacket made with Fuel 3CORE: a fabric with a high abrasion resistance that, together with its protection in the back, shoulders, and elbows, has obtained the European Class AAA and the UKCA certificates. Ripstop fabric 100% Nylon with PU coating that makes it water-repellent, cold resistant and wear resistant to damage from normal usage.

Single layer 3/4 jacket

A 3/4 jacket made with Fuel 3CORE: a fabric with a high abrasion resistancethat, together with its protection in the back, shoulders, and elbows, has obtained the Class AAA CE Certified and the UKCA certificates.

It's all in the details

A small pin on the lapel, a piece of fabric to better close the collar and keep the air out, leather reinforcements at strategic points and a uniquely designed buckle.

Folded rain jacket

4 pockets in the front (two of them large in size) and two in the back, where in one of them you can find a water-resistant jacket folded into a bag in case of rain to wear over the jacket and be protected from water.

PROTECTION TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS

▪ Fuel 3CORE single layer fabric

▪ Removable Smoothways CE level 2 protectors on the back, elbows, and shoulders

▪ Packable rain jacket

▪ YKK double rack zipper

▪ CE EN17092-3:2020 Class AAA certified

▪ UKCA certified

What is Fuel 3CORE Fabric?

Technology is changing and growing fast. This is why after two years of development, we developed the FUEL 3CORE fabric, to guarantee customer satisfaction and improve our products.

Fuel 3CORE fabric is produced with leading-edge tri-core technology: a new revolutionary technology resulting in a lighter fabric with significantly improved performance in both strength and comfort. The Fuel 3CORE single layer is an abrasion-resistant fabric with bi-stretch exclusively developed for our products, so you can leave the main road safer, lighter, and even more comfortable.

Imagine a flat piece of land with an oval-shaped track on it. Young people hungry for speed, pushing their limits to see who can go around the fastest without brakes. Flat track racing has been around for nearly a century and it is possibly the oldest form of motorcycle racing still in existence. The Fuel "Sidewaze" leather jacket pays homage to those times and spirit.

Thanks to the high-quality buffalo suede leather, this jacket not only protects but also gains a unique patina as it ages over the course of time. The jackets are waxed individually, giving each one a unique character.

The Fuel Sidewaze Jacket sizes slightly smaller than similar leather jackets. Please check and follow the size guide below. If you're between sizes, pick one size larger.

PROTECTION / TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS

100% Full grain Buffalo suede leather outer shell

100% Full grain Naturally tanned black leather sleeves

300 GSM 100% Cotton twill inner shell.

CE approved elbow shoulder and back protectors Level 2

YKK japanese made brass zippers

Nickel-free brass buttons

Waxed processing for pronounced badass look

CE approved prEN 17092-4:2020 Class AAA + UKCA

By spring of 1924, Camberley, Great Britain was hosting the first ever, official scramble.

In time, the official name for the entire sport itself became, “motocross.” The word was derived from “motocyclette” which is motorcycle in French, and the combined words “cross country.”

The “Dust Devil” boots are a tribute to a time when motocross was taking its first steps, when everything was still to be explored and developed, an exciting moment that would later lead to one of the most popular motor sports in the world.

Technical specs

Natural crazy horse leather construction with suede leather on the front part of the boot. Crazy Horse leather is made from full-grain cowhide. A coating of natural wax is applied to the leather that gets better and more beautiful with time and usage.

Built-in impact absorption material to provide protection in the shin and ankle area.

Waterproof membrane to keep your feet dry

Reinforcement in the heel area to stabilize heel position.

Durable compound rubber outsole with anti-slip treatment.

CE Approved. EN13634:2017

Introducing the Sergeant 2 Pants, highly functional riding trousers that not only look like they can take a beating, but that can perform too. The 2nd generation of Fuel's highly popular Sergeant Pants keeps the same look but with a much-improved fit. These fit much more true-to-size than the original Sergeant's. In addition, the knee armour can be adjusted up or down if needed. Quilting and suede panels give the Sergeant 2 a style of their own. This new version also comes with the FUEL 3CORE fabric, produced with leading-edge tri-core technology.

PROTECTION TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS

Fuel 3CORE single layer fabric

Supplied with Level 2 knee and hip armour

New adjustable knee protections.

CE/UKCA Certification AAA - highest in the market (EN 17092-2:2020 CLASS AAA)

Fitting reviewed and improved - now much more true-to-size.

Strengthened seams: with double stitching.

Introducing the new and upgraded Fuel “Division 2” jacket. A 1950s-inspired design that combines the classic looks of yesteryear with all the benefits of modern technology.

Made using tough military canvas with a water and dirt repellent treatment, and detailed with supple suede in high-use areas. Improved pattern with longer arm length for a more comfortable fit, and a waterproof lining for riding in rainy conditions.

Three large waterproof pockets and one waterproof document pocket. A brown corduroy collar for a greater feel and style, with a high-quality neck closure using traditional leather and brass fittings.

A zip-out black liner creates insulation during the winter but can be removed in the warmer months for optimum year-round comfort. Zipped ventilation openings on the sleeves and across the shoulder at the rear create all-important airflow on that dusty track to nowhere.

Vintage style with no compromise, supplied with smooth ways CE level 2 body armor at the elbow, shoulder, and spine. Can you hear the call of the wild?

Tech Specs

100% Cotton canvas black colored outer shell

Cow Suede Leather

Cotton blend Polyester fabric Burgundy color inner

125g Thermo liner (removable)

Waterproof membrane

Reinforced with Kevlar in impact areas

Includes Smoothways CE level 2 body armor at elbows, shoulders, and spine

Waxed cotton for water resistance

Fitment note: our customers usually find these fit on the small side so you may wish to consider sizing up from what you normally wear.

The Rainer Suit is your go-to choice for staying dry and comfortable in challenging weather conditions. This waterproof ensemble, consisting of a jacket and pants, is not only stylish in khaki but also packed with features to enhance your outdoor experience.

Designed with an oversized cut, this suit is thoughtfully crafted to be worn comfortably over your jacket. We recommend choosing your regular size for the ideal fit.

Key Features.

Total Waterproofing: Crafted with precision and featuring thermally sealed seams, the Rainer Suit is your ultimate defense against rain, keeping you completely dry in the wettest of conditions.

Stay Visible: The Rainer Suit features reflective trim that enhances your visibility, ensuring you're seen even in low-light conditions, making it perfect for those evening rides.

Ready for Any Adventure: Whether you're hiking in the woods, biking through puddle-filled trails, or simply braving a rainy day, the Rainer Suit is designed to keep you dry and stylish, no matter the adventure.

Package dimensions with the rain suit inside packed: 25cm x 32cm, and the weight is approximately 840g.

Tech specs:

Adjustable neck, cuffs and bottom pant

Outer Fabric: 100% Waterproof Polyester

Sealed stitches to block water absorption

High-quality velcro to keep the water out

Reflective panels on sleeves and bottom pant

Waterproof patch pockets on jacket and pant with velcro and tape to open

Elastic with cords on waistband hoodie

The re-edition of a classic, the Fuel “New Stripes” is inspired by characters like “Chino” from the film The Wild One, movies about motorcycle gangs who rode their Harleys across the country on endless straights going from town to town. A way of living that you can relive with this t-shirt! Go Wild!

Made with the finest Portuguese cotton produced locally and sustainably, this T-shirt is LIMITED EDITION - once she gone, she gone!

Fuel x Scalpers Collection - Limited Edition

A tried and true, go-to sweatshirt for all seasons. This fleece sweatshirt is made of cotton, making it one of the softest and most comfortable garments you'll ever wear. With a roomy cut and overlock seams, this striped sweatshirt is sure to become your favorite. Made of 100% cotton fleece with printed logo and contrast overlock seams.

If you love the feeling of freedom and risk, this collection inspired by the motorcycle beach races of the 50s, is for you.

These pants are made of high-quality denim mixed witharamid which means they are lighter and more comfortable than other denim pants that have aramid panels. Thanks to their vintage design, there is only one truth: You can wear them whenever you want.

The Pants are made with the same technical specifications and unique design as the jacket. For your maximum safety, the pants offer protection at the hips and knees. The pants are a real eye-catcher, especially on the back. The stitches on the pockets look like curved roads, and the waistband includes a stylish suede logo.

To be honest: There are not many pants that make you dream of your next trip. But this one definitely makes dreams come true.

➖ Tech specs ➖

▪ 14oz denim mixed with DuPont™ Kevlar® fiber (Single layer)

▪ Tappered bottom legs

▪ CE approved level 2 knee and hip protectors

▪ CE approved prEN 17092-4:2017 Class AA

NEW FUEL MARSHAL PANTS

We are proud to introduce the most comfortable and best-fitting pants ever, no matter your shape.

***We find the Marshal Pants tend to fit small. You may want to go up a size from what you normally wear particularly if you’re in between sizes***

Thanks to the side gusset, they adapt to any rider’s body shape, and not only that, the pants are made of Fuel 3CORE fabric, so your safety is guaranteed with the maximum AAA Class certification. So, in short, these pants are the perfect combination of comfort and safety never before seen in the motorcycle market.

The Racing Division Jersey is inspired by vintage Enduro racers and designed especially for aggressive off-road riders, our jerseys have been tested in the toughest conditions. Spread the competition spirit with the Racing Division Collection.

Each jersey is made using High IQ® Cool Comfort technology. This allows our riders to remain comfortable in a wide range of conditions and temperatures. Get an unfair advantage out on the track and do it in style wearing a Fuel Motorcycles Jersey.

▪ Mesh pit vent panels for maximum airflow to high-sweat areas

▪ Comfortable and soft, with a quick-dry/dry-touch feeling

▪ Stains wash out easily

▪ Body-mapped fabric placement
